Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Borders
    The class is for the appearance of the borders.
    Bullets
    The main class for controlling the functionality of the bullets such as speed, color, and size.
    Game
    An abstract Game class.

    The default controls are for "Player 1" to move left and right with the 'A' and 'D' keys, up and down with the 'W' and 'S' keys, and shoot with the space key.

    Before the Game begins, the setup method is executed.
    GameObject
    An abstract class for an object which can be added to an instance of Game

    The act method can be implemented to provide a behavior for the object, and will be called every millisecond automatically by a Game it has been added to.
    Main
    This is the main class that is used to run the whole game and has the functionality of the zombies, bullets, player and etc.
    Player
    The class for the functionality of the players where it controls how the player is moving where it contains the up, down, left, and right key detection.
    ZombieMovement
    The class that controls the functionality of the zombie movements.
    ZombieType
    The main class for where it controls the functionality of the zombie types within the game, controls the health, speed.
